'''''Gupfa Storie van Klara Viljee''''' '''(The Story of Klara Viljee),''' ni filimi yasohotse muri 1992 muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Epfo iyoborwa na Katinka Heyns na vyahinguwe n'Ivyabona Chris Barnard kuko Sonneblom Films<ref>https://mubi.com/films/die-storie-van-klara-viljee</ref><ref>https://www.worldcat.org/title/storie-van-klara-viljee/oclc/699482591</ref>.  Muri iyi filime hagaragaramo Anna-Mart van der Merwe mu mwanya wa mbere hamwe na Regardt van den Bergh, Hennie Oosthuizen na Trix Pienaar mu nshingano zabo<ref>http://vetseun.co.za/anarkans/film/filmdiestorievanklaraviljee.html</ref><ref>https://openjournals.uwaterloo.ca/index.php/kinema/article/view/1311/1712</ref>.  

Iyi filime ivuga ku buzima bwa Klara Viljee, umukobwa wo mu mudugudu muto wo kuroba igihe yabuze se n'umukunzi we mu nyanja. Filime yakiriwe neza kandi yegukana ibihembo byinshi mubirori mpuzamahanga bya firime.<ref>https://booksagain.co.za/paljas-die-storie-van-klara-viljee-die-filmdraaiboeke.html</ref><ref>https://networthpost.org/net-worth/katinka-heyns-net-worth/</ref>

